# Review State Migrations

Place forward-only SQLite migration files for review execution state in this directory when the review-state schema changes.

Rules:
- use zero-padded numeric prefixes such as `0002_add_reviewer_group.sql`
- keep migrations idempotent where possible
- do not edit already-applied migration files
- update `review_state_schema.sql` so fresh projects still bootstrap correctly from scratch
- rerun `uv run python tools/init_review_state.py` after adding a migration
